# 🏠 House Price Prediction – UI/UX Implementation

## 📖 Project Description

This project predicts house prices using a trained Machine Learning model.
The model takes inputs such as **square footage, number of bathrooms, number of balconies, and distance to the metro station**, and displays the predicted price through a **Streamlit web interface**.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Predict house prices using a trained ML model
* Interactive web interface using Streamlit
* User-friendly number input fields
* Displays predicted price in **Lakhs and Rupees**
* Shows affordability status (**Affordable / Expensive**)

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* Python
* Streamlit
* NumPy
* Pickle
* Scikit-learn (for model training)
* VS Code (for development)

